Supported Distributions

Thomas Roh

May 5, 2017

Source: vignettes/univariate_distributions.Rmd
univariate_distributions.Rmd

Supported Automated Fitting of Distributions

  • Discrete Distributions
    • Empirical (empDis)
    • Geometric (geom)
    • Negative Binomial (nbinom)
    • Poisson (pois)
    • Uniform (dunif)
  • Continuous Distributions
    • Empirical (empCont)
    • Exponential (exp)
    • Gamma (gamma)
    • Inverse Gamma (invgamma)
    • Inverse Gaussian (invgauss)
      • Wald
    • Inverse Weibull (invweibull)
    • Log Logistic (llogis)
      • Fisk
    • Logistic (logis)
    • Lognormal (lnorm)
    • Normal (norm)
    • Uniform (unif)
    • Weibull (weibull)
